706779f-b.title: Brooklyn: Shore Road - 80th Street
706779f-b.text:
(1)
Shore Road, at the S.E. corner of 80th Street, showing the Rulef
J. Van Brunt house, known later as "owl's Head", (This house appears
on maps of 1916 with certain changes, however it does not appear in the
1929 real estate Atlas).  1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
(2)
The same, from a different angle.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
(3)
The same, another view.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
